title: Realism and Tradition in Art, 1848-1900 (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Realism and Tradition in Art, 1848-1900
Prentice-Hall | 1966 | ISBN: N/A | English | 210 pages | PDF | 31.4 MB

Through a broad selection of familiar central documents and less well-knownmones, the author has focused upon the problems faced by innovators in all realms of thought and action in the middle of the 19th century. This book brings a fresh approach to the struggle, in both art and politics, between the established order and the forces of change
